>my work for what reason? 
>
>反応が違いますね。
>どうやら何か仕事をしているようです。
>早速聞き込みを．．
>
>You say, 'What work'
>
>a frost giant wolf tamer says 'Do you not see the wolves?  I train 
>them.  I break them of their pride and make them into useful 
>servants.  Only when they willingly accept the harness are they 
>useful. 
>
>You say, 'What harness'
>
>a frost giant wolf tamer says 'Aye.  Good metal.  We make their 
>harnesses and wraps here in Kael from strong black steel.  You can't 
>break a beast without a good strong harness.  I've learned that from 
>years of working with them. 
>
