>してみましょう。
>
>a frost giant wolf tamer says 'Ahhh.  Now this is interesting 
>indeed.  I see.  Crafty little ice gnats.  Here, perhaps you can find 
>use for one of our harnesses.  Fair trade eh?  If you want more work 
>let me know. 
>
>Blood Wolf Harnessが貰えます。
>（ちなみにGDのDrakkal Dire Wolfから取れる物と同一なので、それを持っていれ
